&lt;p&gt;The CTLgrads Journal Club will be a HyFlex event,&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;you may choose to attend either in person OR&amp;nbsp;online via Zoom&lt;/strong&gt;. Journal Club will&amp;nbsp;start&amp;nbsp;on &lt;strong&gt;Tuesday 2/21&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;from &lt;strong&gt;2:40-3:55pm&lt;/strong&gt; and&amp;nbsp;will meet every other Tuesday through April (2/21, 3/7, 3/21, 4/4, 4/18).&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
