&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;ldquo;Analog genomics: Transcriptional dosage effects in human variation and disease&amp;rdquo;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3:30pm Adrian Veres&lt;/strong&gt; (Harvard University, MA)&lt;/p&gt;
