&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Isabelle Grangaud &lt;/strong&gt;(CNRS Research Professor, Norbert Elias Center, Marseille),&amp;nbsp;&amp;ldquo;Investigating the Algerian Ottoman Collection: Archives, Conflicts, Colonization&amp;rdquo;&lt;/p&gt;
