&lt;p&gt;Are you or a loved one currently dealing with a cancer diagnosis? Feeling lost in all the new terminology and decisions you are having to make? At Columbia Cancer, we know that being diagnosed with cancer can be overwhelming. We are here to help you navigate this challenging time.&lt;br /&gt;
