&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Acceptance and Rejection in the Career Space | Design Your Next Steps (Virtual)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have you accepted a job/internship offer? Have you received a rejection from an employer for a job/internship? Perhaps, you did not hear back from an employer at all?&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
