&lt;p&gt;The&amp;nbsp;Center for Sexual and Gender Minority Health Research and the Center for Health Policy presents,&lt;strong&gt; &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;quot;Attack on bodily autonomy: health policy, anti-trans legislation, and the fall of Roe,&amp;quot; a&amp;nbsp;panel discussion via zoom, with an in-person viewing event followed by a reception at the School of Nursing, 7th floor event space.&lt;br /&gt;
