&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Olga Rudenko&lt;/strong&gt; is the chief editor of the Kyiv Independent, an award-winning media start-up launched in November 2021 by the former editorial team of the Kyiv Post. Olga is the former deputy chief editor of the Kyiv Post. She has written for global publications, and was a fellow at the Chicago Booth School of Business in 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
