European Commission Executive Vice President for the European Green Deal&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;and&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="https://www.sipa.columbia.edu/faculty-research/faculty-directory/jason-bordoff" target="_blank"&gt;Jason Bordoff&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
