&lt;p&gt;The conversation will be moderated by award-winning CBS medical correspondent Dr. Max Gomez. Attendees will have a chance to submit questions to the panelists. &lt;a href="https://columbiacuimc.zoom.us/webinar/register/WN_TQXMeTNiTQOCnmAF3HNw3A" target="_blank"&gt;Register for the webinar here.&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
