&lt;p&gt;Dr. Erden has been teaching economics courses at Columbia University since 2010. Her focus is on Econometrics, Macroeconometrics, and Applied Econometrics. She holds a B.A. in Economics from Bogazici University, in Istanbul, Turkey. Her M.A. and Ph.D. degrees are from the University of Wisconsin, Milwaukee.&lt;/p&gt;
