&lt;a href="https://journalism.columbia.edu/faculty/june-cross" target="_blank"&gt;June Cross&lt;/a&gt;, Professor of Journalism; Director of the Documentary Journalism Program; author of the new play&amp;nbsp;&lt;em&gt;Douglass the Prophet,&lt;/em&gt; showing at Harlem Stage from March 31-April 1, starring Emmy Award-winning actor Keith David&lt;br /&gt;
